      },
      {
        "content": "The chunk is not from the main article content but from a separate MIT Press Reader page titled \"How Nintendo Bled Atari Games to Death.\" The page frames the piece with the tagline \"Behind every great console is a great legal fight,\" and lists Julien Mailland as the author with the publication date Apr 15, 2025. This appears to be a navigation or related-article fragment rather than content from Philippe's target article, so it mainly adds source context.",
