      {
        "content": "I (agent) notice that this chunk likely signals the ingestion process has reached an unrelated page or footer fragment. Because it does not continue Lemarchand's argument about design and storytelling, it should be stored only as context about the source page rather than as part of the Philippe article narrative. That helps preserve continuity without contaminating the memory archive with unrelated material.",
